&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Template:POTD/2016-12-06&quot; title=&quot;Template:POTD/2016-12-06&quot;&gt;Gilt-bronze Maitreya in Meditation (National Treasure No. 83)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
