	<entry>
		<id>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:FeedItem/potd/20161211000000/en</id>
		<title>Wikipedia picture of the day for December 11</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:FeedItem/potd/20161211000000/en"/>
				<updated>2016-12-11T00:00:00Z</updated>
		
		<summary type="html">&lt;table style=&quot;margin:0 3px 3px; width:100%; text-align:left; background-color:transparent; border-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&quot;padding:0 0.9em 0 0;&quot;&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/File:Spanish_Civil_War_-_Mass_grave_-_Est%C3%A9par,_Burgos.jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; title=&quot;Mass grave&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Mass grave&quot; src=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9a/Spanish_Civil_War_-_Mass_grave_-_Est%C3%A9par%2C_Burgos.jpg/380px-Spanish_Civil_War_-_Mass_grave_-_Est%C3%A9par%2C_Burgos.jpg&quot; width=&quot;380&quot; height=&quot;257&quot; srcset=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9a/Spanish_Civil_War_-_Mass_grave_-_Est%C3%A9par%2C_Burgos.jpg/570px-Spanish_Civil_War_-_Mass_grave_-_Est%C3%A9par%2C_Burgos.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9a/Spanish_Civil_War_-_Mass_grave_-_Est%C3%A9par%2C_Burgos.jpg/760px-Spanish_Civil_War_-_Mass_grave_-_Est%C3%A9par%2C_Burgos.jpg 2x&quot; data-file-width=&quot;4852&quot; data-file-height=&quot;3280&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&quot;padding:0 6px 0 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Mass_grave&quot; title=&quot;Mass grave&quot;&gt;mass grave&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; of 26 &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Republican_faction_(Spanish_Civil_War)&quot; title=&quot;Republican faction (Spanish Civil War)&quot;&gt;Republican&lt;/a&gt; victims killed by &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Nationalist_faction_(Spanish_Civil_War)&quot; title=&quot;Nationalist faction (Spanish Civil War)&quot;&gt;Nationalists&lt;/a&gt; in 1936 during the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Spanish_Civil_War&quot; title=&quot;Spanish Civil War&quot;&gt;Spanish Civil War&lt;/a&gt;. This grave was excavated in &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Est%C3%A9par&quot; title=&quot;Estépar&quot;&gt;Estépar&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Burgos&quot; title=&quot;Burgos&quot;&gt;Burgos&lt;/a&gt;, in 2014.
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Generally speaking, mass graves contain multiple bodies that may or may not be identified prior to burial. They may be seen after violent conflict or be dug for sanitation reasons after a major &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Famine&quot; title=&quot;Famine&quot;&gt;famine&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Epidemic&quot; title=&quot;Epidemic&quot;&gt;epidemic&lt;/a&gt;, or &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Natural_disaster&quot; title=&quot;Natural disaster&quot;&gt;natural disaster&lt;/a&gt;.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;small&gt;Photograph: &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/User:Mario_modesto&quot; title=&quot;User:Mario modesto&quot;&gt;Mario Modesto Mata&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
