		<title>Wikipedia picture of the day for December 16</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:FeedItem/potd/20161216000000/en"/>
				<updated>2016-12-16T00:00:00Z</updated>
		
		<summary type="html">&lt;table style=&quot;margin:0 3px 3px; width:100%; text-align:left; background-color:transparent; border-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&quot;padding:0 0.9em 0 0;&quot;&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/File:William_Simpson_-_George_Zobel_-_England_and_America._The_visit_of_her_majesty_Queen_Victoria_to_the_Arctic_ship_Resolute_-_December_16th,_1856.jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; title=&quot;HMS Resolute&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;HMS Resolute&quot; src=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/2a/William_Simpson_-_George_Zobel_-_England_and_America._The_visit_of_her_majesty_Queen_Victoria_to_the_Arctic_ship_Resolute_-_December_16th%2C_1856.jpg/380px-William_Simpson_-_George_Zobel_-_England_and_America._The_visit_of_her_majesty_Queen_Victoria_to_the_Arctic_ship_Resolute_-_December_16th%2C_1856.jpg&quot; width=&quot;380&quot; height=&quot;266&quot; srcset=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/2a/William_Simpson_-_George_Zobel_-_England_and_America._The_visit_of_her_majesty_Queen_Victoria_to_the_Arctic_ship_Resolute_-_December_16th%2C_1856.jpg/570px-William_Simpson_-_George_Zobel_-_England_and_America._The_visit_of_her_majesty_Queen_Victoria_to_the_Arctic_ship_Resolute_-_December_16th%2C_1856.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/2a/William_Simpson_-_George_Zobel_-_England_and_America._The_visit_of_her_majesty_Queen_Victoria_to_the_Arctic_ship_Resolute_-_December_16th%2C_1856.jpg/760px-William_Simpson_-_George_Zobel_-_England_and_America._The_visit_of_her_majesty_Queen_Victoria_to_the_Arctic_ship_Resolute_-_December_16th%2C_1856.jpg 2x&quot; data-file-width=&quot;9856&quot; data-file-height=&quot;6912&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&quot;padding:0 6px 0 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Queen_Victoria&quot; title=&quot;Queen Victoria&quot;&gt;Queen Victoria&lt;/a&gt; visits &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/HMS_Resolute_(1850)&quot; title=&quot;HMS Resolute (1850)&quot;&gt;HMS &lt;i&gt;Resolute&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; prior to the ship being granted to her as a gift. &lt;i&gt;Resolute&lt;/i&gt; was a British ship abandoned in the Arctic ice in 1854. She was found adrift by American whalers the following year, refurbished, and returned to the British. As a return favour, when the ship was broken up in 1879, some of its wood was made into a desk and gifted to the US President &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Rutherford_B._Hayes&quot; title=&quot;Rutherford B. Hayes&quot;&gt;Rutherford B. Hayes&lt;/a&gt;. The &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Resolute_desk&quot; title=&quot;Resolute desk&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;Resolute&lt;/i&gt; desk&lt;/a&gt; remains an iconic part of the American White House furniture.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Lithograph&quot; class=&quot;mw-redirect&quot; title=&quot;Lithograph&quot;&gt;Lithograph&lt;/a&gt;: George Zobel, after &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/William_Simpson_(artist)&quot; title=&quot;William Simpson (artist)&quot;&gt;William Simpson&lt;/a&gt;; restoration: &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/User:Adam_Cuerden&quot; title=&quot;User:Adam Cuerden&quot;&gt;Adam Cuerden&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
